      Parameters:
      image - Constructor of GranuloData object, it instanciate Measures with process(image) and image with this.Image Date and Time will be instanciate with the current date & time with java.time.LocalDate.now() and java.time.LocalTime.now() set grain Scale with default value (setScale(min,max))

  • Method Details

    • process

      public MeasuresList process(javafx.scene.image.Image image)
      Parameters:
      image -
      Returns:
      the measures list after the image Traitement (CCLabeler.getMeasure) the methods store an image in ImageToProcessList object. It addImageName(image.getUrl()) will put this in ImageToProcessList's LinkedList after that, the methods create an CCLabeler object. Then, for each Image in the list, it past the images url in the CCLabeler. Finally it return CCLabeler.getMeasure
